{"tid":1854733,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"TrySail討論區15 トラハモ再出發","createTime":"2020-01-31T15:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T09:41:36.000Z","uid":280300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"85554049aadf48234b1958bd37fa04f3381b628b","tid":1854733,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1UVH7F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1UVH7F.jpg&h=4a7b365f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTrySail是Music Ray'n所屬的女性聲優組合，成員為麻倉桃、雨宮天和夏川椎菜。唱片公司為SACRA MUSIC。<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n組合的三位成員是2012年第二屆Music Ray'n超級聲優試鏡（ミュージックレイン スーパー声優オーディション）合格而進入Music Ray'n事務所的。2014年1月7日開始三人開設了廣播節目&ldquo;TRYangle harmony&rdquo;。近一年後的2014年12月21日，在TRYangle harmony的活動上宣布三人結成組合TrySail、2015年活動開始；廣播亦於2015年第一期更名為&ldquo;TrySailのTRYangle harmony&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n組合名TrySail(トライセイル)為雨宮天提出。英語中trysail指帆船在大風時用的小帆，而其中的&ldquo;try&rdquo;也與&ldquo;TRYangle harmony&rdquo;相合，可以指&ldquo;嘗試&rdquo;以及&ldquo;3&rdquo;等。<br />\n<br />\n2015年5月13日發售了出道單曲Youthful Dreamer（動畫《電波教師》OP）。<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月，發行TrySail唱片的公司由Aniplex轉為索尼旗下的SACRA MUSIC。<br />\n<br />\n3位成員都同時以個人身份出道。<br />\n<br />\n3位成員在剛出道的2013年曾經在動畫《某科學的超電磁炮S》中一起出演醬油角色。<br />\n<br />\n3位成員都在《偶像大師 百萬現場》中出演，並因此在2014年劇場版動畫《偶像大師 劇場版 走向光輝的未來》中共同出演。<br />\n<br />\n3位成員都以歌手身份出道了。雨宮天比其他兩人歌手出道都要早，單曲也較多（6張，截至2018年7月）。但雨宮天在TrySail活動較為活躍的2016年卻沒有發布任何單曲，直至2017年7月。夏川椎菜和麻倉桃則在2016年至2017年間陸續歌手出道。3人的個人單曲的信息也會一併在TrysailのTRYangle harmony節目最後進行宣傳。"},{"pid":"9a391709c2ab9f93cf57434f0707e095eb1ec826","tid":1854733,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"無人回應?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60b775d2fedebecfd4b981790477d64afad0fee","tid":1854733,"uid":94593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b34487285869f567748ca74348c2009a2b1b5f","tid":1854733,"uid":308375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40e9bdc54d5167909cadf5286223fcab785ef7d9","tid":1854733,"uid":320048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"90b507037b26a76bf4ffc0b0634b522b92ee2396","tid":1854733,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"點解聲優通常唱歌都好聽"},{"pid":"57bf657ca24aaddcbc141d80a9967c4c08285629","tid":1854733,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b507037b26a76bf4ffc0b0634b522b92ee2396","tid":1854733,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"點解聲優通常唱歌都好聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"因為佢地有實力囉, 而唔係睇佢地既外貌"},{"pid":"511bbca1b8a60c9d46530d9eb7b9896bc441b236","tid":1854733,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57bf657ca24aaddcbc141d80a9967c4c08285629","tid":1854733,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b507037b26a76bf4ffc0b0634b522b92ee2396","tid":1854733,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"點解聲優通常唱歌都好聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"因為佢地有實力囉, 而唔係睇佢地既外貌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"但係唱歌好聽嘅人配音又唔一定好"},{"pid":"50a78c6c25ef5ba26e69c0f547101935419662ca","tid":1854733,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,